Package: surveyorso
Title: A comprehensive toolkit for survey research and analytics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Giorgi",
        family = "Buzaladze",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "g.buzaladze@gmail.com"
    )
Description: surveyorso provides a unified set of tools for end-to-end survey research workflows, including metadata handling, automated tabulation, utilities for merging multi-wave datasets, open-ended coding, and advanced analytics. The functions are designed to reduce manual processing, standardize analytics pipelines, and support fully reproducible insights for both single and longitudinal studies. The package follows tidyverse conventions and offers full support for SPSS-style metadata, making it easy to integrate into existing survey-data environments.
